org.opends.server.admin.std.client

Interface RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfgClient

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurationClient, QOSPolicyCfgClient

    public interface RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfgClient
extends QOSPolicyCfgClient
    A client-side interface for reading and modifying Request Filtering QOS Policy settings.

    The Request Filtering QOS Policy is used to define the type of requests allowed by the server.
